author: Republic_Commando_Sev
title: Small but good
review:
This set is small but it comes with a lot! It comes with a window sheild, Takeshi, two guns, and the legs are made out of technic pieces! The reason I give it a three is beacause the cockpit is open. You can shoot the guy right out of the cockpit! Pretty good set!
Republic Commando Sev
